{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/Recognize.gif?t=1737037394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Impostor is a unique social deception game, where you play either as an impostor, pretending to be an AI, or as the detective, who is trying to expose the impostor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The detective picks a question for the impostor to answer. The impostor must write an answer which will sound like it is AI-written. The impostor loses the round if he is exposed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/Guess.gif?t=1737037394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are several game modes, each of which puts a new spin on this system.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Practice Mode -</strong> Hone your human-detection skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Online Mode -</strong> Play with other friends who own the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Local Mode -</strong> Play locally on one computer, taking turns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Streamer Mode -</strong>\u00a0Play with your stream chat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/extras/Deceive.gif?t=1737037394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is currently in the process of being tested and built in public, and should be ready around February.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737037394","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110320/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737037394","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass